      <h1 class="display-1">Inside Sales &amp; Telemarketing: The Sales Path Into Mortgage</h1>
      <p class="lead hero-subtitle">Every great loan officer started on the phone. Inside sales &mdash; what some call telemarketing &mdash; is the entry point to the highest-earning path in the mortgage business. If you're outgoing and can handle rejection, this is where a sales career begins.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <button type="button" data-caf-open class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Start My Mortgage Career</button>
        <a href="#path" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Why It's Step One</a>
      </div>
